title: Who is the rhino on The Masked Singer 2020? - Quora

response.answer_text: Johnny Manziel is the rhino on The Masked Singer.  Johnathan Paul Manziel was born on December 6, 1992. He is a former American football quarterback. He previously played two seasons with the Cleveland Browns of the National Football League (NFL) and was also a member of the Hamilton Tiger-Cats and Montreal Alouettes in the Canadian Football League (CFL) in 2018. He most recently played for the Memphis Express of the Alliance of American Football (AAF). (source: Wikipedia) Thanks for Reading Upvote if you agree with my answer. Follow me if you like my answer. ~Aman
The rhino is Barry Zito. Barry Zito played professional baseball as a pitcher for the Oakland Athletics.
